  </relevant-files>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Resolve today's date (YYYY-MM-DD).</step>
    <step order="2">Ledger audit: load `projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/ledgers/real-bug-ledger.md`; for each of the 20 entries (5 HIGH + 7 MED + 8 LOW from the catalog in design.md §2.2), record current status. EXPECT: zero entries in `open`/`assigned-to-r2`/`in-progress`. Any entry not closed is a HALT.</step>
    <step order="3">Unit-suite confirmation run: `dotnet test tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests.csproj -c Release --logger "trx;LogFileName=phase3-unit-confirmation-{date}.trx" --results-directory projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/baseline/`. Confirm `Failed: 0`.</step>
    <step order="4">Integration-suite cross-reference: read task 038's summary doc (`baseline/phase3-integration-triple-run-{date}.md`); confirm all 3 runs show `Failed: 0`; capture flake count + disposition for this exit-gate doc.</step>
    <step order="5">Per-task NFR-04 audit: for each of tasks 030, 031, 032, 033, 034, 035, 036, 037, find the commit via `git log --grep="RB-T..."`. Confirm message contains the ledger entry ID + resolution mode word (`repaired` / `transferred-to-sibling` / `archived-as-dead-target`). Record commit SHA + message excerpt for each.</step>
    <step order="6">Phase 4 readiness: list the 5 parallel tracks (A: PCF audit, B: Stryker pilot, C: TestClock PoC, D: Coverlet baseline, E: anti-drift report). For each, list inputs needed + external dependencies. Flag Track D as gated on `github-actions-rationalization-r1` Phase 1 (per plan.md §5).</step>
    <step order="7">Write `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/baseline/phase3-exit-{date}.md` with sections: (a) Ledger State; (b) Unit-Suite Confirmation; (c) Integration-Suite Triple-Run; (d) Per-Task Closure Audit; (e) Phase 4 Readiness; (f) Phase 3 Close Declaration.</step>
    <step order="8">Verify `git status` shows only new files in `baseline/` — no `src/`, no `tests/`, no other modifications.</step>
    <step order="9">Update `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/current-task.md` with completion + cite exit doc path + declare Phase 3 closed + next task = first Phase 4 task per `TASK-INDEX.md`.</step>
  </steps>

